desc: An Australian, designer jewellery brand, embodying a paired back aesthetic that is both effortless and conceptual. Created for the modern woman, a love of sun-drenched moments and nostalgic influences comes to life in a curated assembly of effortless essentials, personalised keepsakes and statement pieces.

layout.text: A CREATIVE COLLABORATION BORN OF TWO SUN DRENCHED ISLANDS. INTRODUCING A PLACE IN THE SUN
